{
  "text": "For morphological measurements, embryos were anesthetized with 0.16 mg/mL Tricaine (A5040, Sigma-Aldrich) and embedded in 3% methylcellulose (M0387, Sigma-Aldrich). Body length was measured laterally in the rostral-caudal axis. Eye size was measured laterally along the longest diameter of the eye. Brain size was measured by calculating the dorsal area of the brain using the transgenic line Tg(HuC:GFP) [CITATION_1] .",
